entry.title: Erizur/FNF-DaveEngine
entry.summary:
A Friday Night Funkin' Engine made for the Vs. Dave mod, with additional improvements to make your own mod!

WARNING

THE ENGINE IS AT A VERY UNSTABLE STATE AT THE MOMENT, IT HAS NO MODDING SUPPORT AT THE MOMENT, BUT IT WILL GET ADDED SOON. IF YOU WANNA MAKE A MOD AT THE MOMENT, YOU WILL HAVE TO MODIFY THE SOURCE CODE.

DAVE ENGINE

this is dave

say hi to dave please say hi to him

About the engine

Powered by a heavily modified version of Kade Engine, This includes lots of additional improvements such as

  • OpenGL Shaders
  • Character Selector
  • Languages
  • Strawberry Input

If you're looking to compile the mod/make your own modification, look here.
